                      "mediaType": "image",
                      "src": "media/publish/material_v_4/material_ext_publish/0B6Okdz75tqQsakpNYVp4YnV6b1U/style_typography_styles_14_button2.png"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "module-body",
                  "html": "<p>Chinese, Japanese, and Korean.</p><p><strong>Weight</strong>: Since Noto CJK has seven weights that match Roboto, use the same weight settings as English.</p><p><strong>Font size</strong>: For Title through Caption styles, the font size is 1px larger than that specified for English. For styles larger than Title, the English type size is suitable.</p>"
                },
