        {
          "type": "article",
          "title": "Line height",
          "modules": [
            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "module-body",
                  "html": "<p>To achieve proper readability and appropriate pacing, line heights have been determined based on each style&#x2019;s individual size and weight. Line wrapping only applies to Body, Subhead, Headline, and the smaller Display styles. All other styles should exist as single lines.</p>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
